  "body": "<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/85VBf2K.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1125\" height=\"244\" /></span></span></strong></span></h2>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/isensehostility\"><strong><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://storage.ko-fi.com/cdn/brandasset/kofi_bg_tag_white.png\" alt=\"Buy Me a Coffee at ko-fi.com\" width=\"341\" height=\"129\" border=\"0\" /></span></span></strong></a></span></h2>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">What is Crustaceans?</span></span></strong></span></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #333333;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Crustaceans is a mod that adds a few new creatures to the game. The point of this mod is to make oceans feel more diverse and full of life, whilst maintaining a narrow scope. Instead of adding lots of different kinds of creatures, or even a bunch of sea creatures, the focus is specifically on the crustaceans group.<br /></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff; font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">What does Crustaceans add?</span></strong></span></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #333333;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Crustaceans currently adds two creatures:<br /></span></span></span></p>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</h4>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #3366ff; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Crabs:</strong><br /></span></h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #3366ff; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2Fg2xn6.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></strong></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #3366ff; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Lobsters:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #3366ff; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XAKpDDx.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #333333; font-size: 14px;\">For more information about the creatures check the <a href=\"https://github.com/ISenseHostility/Crustaceans/wiki/Creatures\">wiki</a>.<br /></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #333333; font-size: 14px;\">Crustaceans also adds a new item:</span></p>\n<h4><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #3366ff;\">Claw:</span></strong></span></h4>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/4uBx2Ae.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #333333;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">For more information on the item check the <a href=\"https://github.com/ISenseHostility/Crustaceans/wiki/Items\">wiki</a>.</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #333333;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><br /></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/Hostility\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/partners/custom-banners/f6084c7a-87f3-4946-abff-4917d097a513.png\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">REQUIRES GECKOLIB</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>",
